query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS guest_swipes (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT NOT NULL,
  guest_identifier VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  movie_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  movie_title VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
  movie_poster TEXT,
  movie_type ENUM('movie', 'tv') NOT NULL,
  movie_genres JSON,
  movie_rating DECIMAL(3,1),
  direction ENUM('left', 'right', 'up', 'down') NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES guest_sessions(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  INDEX idx_session_guest (session_id, guest_identifier),
  INDEX idx_movie (movie_id)
)
